OL,3,CHeads of the Valleys road construction
OL,4,Cleaves 'cracks in homes', say locals
OL,6,FPeople living near the new Heads of
OL,7,Fthe Valleys road say their properties
OL,8,Fhave been damaged and they have been
OL,9,Ftreated "absolutely appallingly"
OL,10,Fbecause of the ongoing building work.
OL,12,FThe dual carriageway has been under
OL,13,Fconstruction for a number of years,
OL,14,Fwith work on the current section,
OL,15,FDowlais Top to Hirwaun, starting in
OL,16,F2021.
OL,18,FIt is due to finish in mid-2025 and is
OL,19,Festimated to cost more than a billion
OL,20,Fpounds to complete but should improve
OL,21,Ftraffic and road safety.
