OL,3,CHeads of the Valleys road construction
OL,4,Cleaves 'cracks in homes', say locals
OL,6,FHowever for locals, the disruption
OL,7,Fbuilding work is causing to their
OL,8,Fdaily lives has left many at their
OL,9,Fwit's end - with cracks in their homes
OL,10,Fand high levels of dust outside.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government said it is
OL,13,Fworking with the company in charge of
OL,14,Fbuilding the new road, Future Valleys
OL,15,FConstruction, and the local authority
OL,16,Fto try and fix the issues being raised.
OL,18,FDaryl Wilkins claims the vibrations of
OL,19,Fthe road works have caused cracks in
OL,20,Fevery bedroom of his home and the
OL,21,Fgarage outside.
