OL,6,FHe said he does not want financial
OL,7,Fcompensation, simply for the damage to
OL,8,Fbe fixed.
OL,10,FDaryl said: "Repair the damage that
OL,11,Fthey've done to my property. That's
OL,12,Fall. Nothing else."
OL,14,FFor his wife Ann, the dust is a huge
OL,15,Fproblem and means she cannot sit in
OL,16,Fthe garden or peg the washing out. The
OL,17,Flevel of dust is even putting them out
OL,18,Fof pocket, as they say they have to
OL,19,Fpay for the windows to be cleaned
OL,20,Fregularly.
