OL,6,F"It costs me #18 a month to have my
OL,7,Fwindows cleaned," she said.
OL,9,F"Within two days they're back dirty
OL,10,Fagain. You get really fed up of it.
OL,12,F"You're wiping it down every day, and
OL,13,Fit's back in the same place the
OL,14,Ffollowing day."
OL,16,FNoise is another problem for those
OL,17,Fliving in the nearby area. One of the
OL,18,Fcauses of this has been a piling
OL,19,Fmachine, which is used to make road
OL,20,Ffoundations stable and strong enough
OL,21,Fto support vehicles.
