OL,4,Cleaves 'cracks in homes', say locals
OL,6,FDaryl and Ann's daughter, Julie
OL,7,FWilkins said: "Constant noise,
OL,8,Fconstant piling within an arms width
OL,9,Fof my parents' garden.
OL,11,F"It needs to happen to stop accidents
OL,12,Ffrom happening and people dying on the
OL,13,Froad, but the way Future Valleys
OL,14,FConstruction have gone about it for
OL,15,Fthe residents has been absolutely
OL,16,Fappalling."
